  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3026480/extras/5c24393c9622a6af69c033559e6a1972.poster.avif?t=1757080656\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3026480/extras/5c24393c9622a6af69c033559e6a1972.webm?t=1757080656\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3026480/extras/5c24393c9622a6af69c033559e6a1972.mp4?t=1757080656\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>A beach day is cut short by digging too deep into the sand. <strong>You Have To Climb Out</strong> is a short (~60 minute) puzzle narrative about a frog stuck in a cave system under the beach. <br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Traverse upward through a linear set of puzzles that require clever placement of blocks and some light platforming to create a path back up to the surface<br></li><li>Find mysterious notes left behind by... someone?<br></li><li>Discover why this suspiciously large cavern exists under the beach at all</li></ul>",
